INSERT INTO `traveladvice` (`countryID`, `countryName`, `countryCode`, `countryDescription`, `countryKeywords`, `countryCapital`, `countryMajorCities`, `countryLanguages`, `countryCurrency`, `countryImage`) VALUES
(1, 'Afghanistan', 'AF', 'Nestled in the heart of Asia, Afghanistan is a land of rugged beauty and ancient history. Despite its tumultuous past, it boasts stunning landscapes ranging from towering mountains to fertile valleys. Visitors can explore historic sites like the Bamiyan Buddhas and experience the hospitality of its diverse cultures.', 'Mountains, Kabul, Culture, History, Hospitality', 'Kabul', 'Kabul, Kandahar, Herat, Mazar-i-Sharif', 'Pashto, Dari', 'Afghani', 'https://udayton.edu/magazine/2021/08/images/2108_afganistan_island.jpg'),
(2, 'Albania', 'AL', 'Tucked away in southeastern Europe, Albania is a hidden gem with a rich history and natural wonders. From the ancient ruins of Butrint to the pristine beaches of the Albanian Riviera, it offers a mix of cultural heritage and stunning landscapes. Visitors can also explore vibrant cities like Tirana and experience the warmth of Albanian hospitality.', 'Mountains, Riviera, Ancient, Culture, Ottoman', 'Tirana', 'Tirana, Durrës, Vlorë, Shkodër', 'Albanian', 'Lek', 'https://www.state.gov/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Albania-2218x1406.jpg'),
(3, 'Algeria', 'DZ', 'With its vast Sahara Desert landscapes and Mediterranean coastlines, Algeria offers a tapestry of contrasts and beauty. Rich in history and culture, it boasts ancient Roman ruins like Timgad and diverse landscapes ranging from the Atlas Mountains to the Tassili n\'Ajjer National Park. Visitors can immerse themselves in Berber traditions, sample delicious Algerian cuisine, and explore the vibrant markets of cities like Algiers.', 'Sahara, Culture, History, Cuisine, Heritage', 'Algiers', 'Algiers, Oran, Constantine, Annaba', 'Arabic, Berber', 'Dinar', 'https://www.state.gov/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/shutterstock_11771813523.jpg'),
(4, 'Andorra', 'AD', 'Nestled in the Pyrenees mountains between France and Spain, Andorra is a tiny principality known for its stunning mountain landscapes and tax-free shopping. Visitors can explore charming villages like Andorra la Vella, indulge in outdoor activities like skiing and hiking, and marvel at medieval landmarks such as the Sant Joan de Caselles church.', 'Mountains, Skiing, Shopping, Cuisine, Adventure', 'Andorra la Vella', 'Andorra la Vella, Escaldes-Engordany, Encamp, Sant Julià de Lòria', 'Catalan', 'Euro', 'https://freedomhouse.org/sites/default/files/2020-02/Andorra__Country_portal_shutterstock_1446148013-127_SELECTION.jpg'),
(5, 'Angola', 'AO', 'Located on the west coast of Southern Africa, Angola is a country of diverse landscapes, from pristine beaches along the Atlantic coast to lush rainforests and the arid beauty of the Namib Desert. Despite its troubled past, Angola is emerging as a tourist destination with attractions such as the Kalandula Falls, colonial architecture in Luanda, and wildlife-rich national parks like Quiçama National Park.', 'Safari, Beaches, Music, Culture, Wildlife', 'Luanda', 'Luanda, Huambo, Lobito, Benguela', 'Portuguese', 'Kwanza', 'https://www.thuisvaccinatie.nl/wp-content/uploads/angola-1920x0-c-default.png'),
(6, 'Anguilla', 'AI', 'A tranquil island paradise in the Caribbean, Anguilla is renowned for its pristine white-sand beaches, turquoise waters, and luxurious resorts. Visitors can enjoy water sports like snorkeling and sailing, explore secluded coves, and savor the island\'s vibrant culinary scene, which blends local flavors with international influences.', 'Beaches, Tranquility, Luxury, Cuisine, Sailing', 'The Valley', 'The Valley', 'English', 'East Caribbean Dollar', 'https://www.travelandleisure.com/thmb/HZwBXTkzXKhrUUPHEPB9N5vhedU=/1500x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/TAL-shoal-bay-TODOANGUILLA0723-18c347b622c642bf88eaa9be74981edc.jpg'),
(7, 'Antigua & Barbuda', 'AG', 'This twin-island nation in the Caribbean is renowned for its stunning beaches, vibrant culture, and rich history. Antigua boasts 365 beaches—one for each day of the year—where visitors can relax on powdery white sands or indulge in water sports like snorkeling and sailing. Meanwhile, Barbuda offers a more secluded retreat, with pristine pink beaches and abundant wildlife, including the famous Frigate Bird Sanctuary.', 'Beaches, Sailing, Luxury, History, Carnival', 'St. John\'s', 'St. John\'s, All Saints, Liberta', 'English', 'East Caribbean Dollar', 'https://a.cdn-hotels.com/gdcs/production111/d641/9f5687f8-b1a2-4ace-8e71-fb2586461290.jpg?impolicy=fcrop&w=800&h=533&q=medium'),
(8, 'Argentina', 'AR', 'From the vibrant streets of Buenos Aires to the breathtaking landscapes of Patagonia, Argentina offers a diverse array of experiences. Tango performances in Buenos Aires, the majestic Iguazú Falls, the otherworldly landscapes of the Andes Mountains, and the rugged beauty of Argentine Patagonia are just a few highlights. Culinary delights such as Argentine beef and Malbec wine further enrich the visitor\'s experience in this vast and captivating country.', 'Tango, Steak, Wine, Patagonia, Football', 'Buenos Aires', 'Buenos Aires, Córdoba, Rosario, Mendoza', 'Spanish', 'Peso', 'https://www.thetimes.co.uk/imageserver/image/%2Fmethode%2Ftimes%2Fprod%2Fweb%2Fbin%2F9a95117e-6bf1-4b42-ac77-b1a412f3b73d.jpg?crop=5000%2C3333%2C0%2C0'),
(9, 'Armenia', 'AM', 'Nestled in the Caucasus region between Europe and Asia, Armenia is a land of ancient history, stunning landscapes, and warm hospitality. Visitors can explore UNESCO World Heritage sites like the Geghard Monastery and the Temple of Garni, hike through the dramatic scenery of the Armenian Highlands, and sample traditional cuisine such as lavash (flatbread) and dolma (stuffed grape leaves).', 'History, Monasteries, Hospitality, Cuisine, Culture', 'Yerevan', 'Yerevan, Gyumri, Vanadzor, Hrazdan', 'Armenian', 'Dram', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/976/cpsprodpb/9AEA/production/_129285693_gettyimages-853983104.jpg'),
(10, 'Aruba', 'AW', 'Situated in the southern Caribbean, Aruba is known for its stunning beaches, vibrant culture, and warm, sunny weather year-round. Visitors can unwind on the powdery white sands of Eagle Beach, explore colorful underwater marine life while snorkeling or diving, and experience the lively atmosphere of Oranjestad, the capital city, with its Dutch colonial architecture and bustling markets.', 'Beaches, Diving, Windsurfing, Cuisine, Carnival', 'Oranjestad', 'Oranjestad, Noord, Santa Cruz, San Nicolas', 'Dutch, Papiamento', 'Aruban florin', 'https://www.vakantiediscounter.nl/blog/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/wat-te-doen-aruba.jpg'),
(11, 'Australia', 'AU', 'The vast continent of Australia offers an abundance of natural wonders, from the iconic Sydney Opera House and Harbour Bridge to the majestic Great Barrier Reef and the rugged Outback. Visitors can explore vibrant cities like Sydney, Melbourne, and Brisbane, encounter unique wildlife such as kangaroos and koalas, and immerse themselves in Indigenous culture and ancient landscapes.', 'Outback, Beaches, Wildlife, Cities, Surfing', 'Canberra', 'Sydney, Melbourne, Brisbane, Perth', 'English', 'Australian Dollar', 'https://content.r9cdn.net/rimg/dimg/43/4b/72c43e11-city-2258-17a3a42c3ab.jpg?crop=true&width=1366&height=768&xhint=1597&yhint=1522'),
(12, 'Austria', 'AT', 'Nestled in the heart of Europe, Austria is a land of alpine beauty, rich history, and cultural heritage. Visitors can marvel at architectural masterpieces like Vienna\'s Schönbrunn Palace and Salzburg\'s Hohensalzburg Fortress, ski in the Tyrolean Alps, and enjoy the musical legacy of composers like Mozart and Strauss in cities renowned for classical music and opera.', 'Alps, Music, History, Architecture, Skiing', 'Vienna', 'Vienna, Graz, Linz, Salzburg', 'German', 'Euro', 'https://content.r9cdn.net/rimg/dimg/a8/ce/6d1490d1-city-64466-16510215367.jpg?width=1366&height=768&xhint=1426&yhint=1115&crop=true'),
(13, 'Azerbaijan', 'AZ', 'Situated at the crossroads of Europe and Asia, Azerbaijan is a country of contrasts, blending ancient traditions with modernity. Visitors can explore the historic streets of Baku\'s Old City, marvel at the futuristic Flame Towers, and discover the natural beauty of places like the mud volcanoes of Gobustan and the Caucasus Mountains.', 'Cuisine, Silk Road, Architecture, Culture, Caspian', 'Baku', 'Baku, Ganja, Sumqayit, Mingachevir', 'Azerbaijani', 'Manat', 'https://keystoneacademic-res.cloudinary.com/image/upload/v1696411259/articles/educationscom/article-hero-image-2991.jpg'),
(14, 'Bahamas', 'BS', 'A tropical paradise in the Atlantic Ocean, the Bahamas is renowned for its stunning beaches, clear turquoise waters, and vibrant coral reefs. Visitors can relax on the powdery sands of Nassau\'s Cable Beach, swim with dolphins in Freeport, or explore the secluded cays and islands of the Exumas.', 'Beaches, Coral, Luxury, Paradise, Music', 'Nassau', 'Nassau, Freeport, West End, Coopers Town', 'English', 'Bahamian Dollar', 'https://www.kayak.nl/rimg/dimg/db/25/fd914ac8-city-11232-1708c88cf11.jpg?width=1366&height=768&xhint=2270&yhint=1918&crop=true'),
(15, 'Bahrain', 'BH', 'A small island nation in the Arabian Gulf, Bahrain is known for its rich history, modern skyline, and cultural heritage. Visitors can explore ancient archaeological sites like the Bahrain Fort and Barbar Temple, shop in bustling souks, and relax on the beaches of Amwaj Islands or Al Jazair.', 'Pearls, Culture, Hospitality, Skyscrapers, Formula1', 'Manama', 'Manama, Riffa, Muharraq, Hamad Town', 'Arabic', 'Bahraini Dinar', 'https://statemag.state.gov/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/cropped-0120POM-17.jpg'),
(16, 'Bangladesh', 'BD', 'Located in South Asia, Bangladesh is a land of rivers, lush greenery, and vibrant culture. Visitors can explore historic sites like the Sundarbans mangrove forest, home to the Bengal tiger, and the ancient city of Paharpur, as well as experience the hustle and bustle of cities like Dhaka and Chattogram.\n', 'Rivers, Culture, Cuisine, Sundarbans, Heritage', 'Dhaka', 'Dhaka, Chittagong, Khulna, Rajshahi', 'Bengali', 'Taka', 'https://dynamic-media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/04/c3/86/03/paharpur-buddhist-monastery.jpg?w=1200&h=1200&s=1'),
(17, 'Barbados', 'BB', 'A Caribbean island nation, Barbados is known for its beautiful beaches, vibrant culture, and colonial architecture. Visitors can relax on the pristine sands of Crane Beach, explore historic plantations like St. Nicholas Abbey, and immerse themselves in the lively atmosphere of Bridgetown, the capital city.\n', 'Beaches, Rum, Music, Cricket, Festivals', 'Bridgetown', 'Bridgetown, Speightstown, Oistins, Bathsheba', 'English', 'Barbadian Dollar', 'https://www.kayak.nl/rimg/dimg/62/45/9f8e96e2-city-24905-1798a9e9030.jpg?width=1366&height=768&xhint=2837&yhint=1711&crop=true'),
(18, 'Belarus', 'BY', 'Situated in Eastern Europe, Belarus is known for its dense forests, picturesque villages, and Soviet-era architecture. Visitors can explore historic sites like Mir Castle and Nesvizh Palace, wander through the charming streets of Minsk, and experience the warm hospitality of its people.\n', 'Forests, Lakes, Culture, History, Hospitality', 'Minsk', 'Minsk, Gomel, Mogilev, Vitebsk', 'Belarusian, Russian', 'Belarusian Ruble', 'https://www.state.gov/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/shutterstock_150664154v2-2109x1406.jpg'),
(19, 'Belgium', 'BE', 'Located in Western Europe, Belgium is famous for its medieval towns, delicious chocolates, and world-renowned beer. Visitors can explore the historic city centers of Brussels, Bruges, and Ghent, marvel at architectural gems like the Grand Place, and indulge in culinary delights such as moules-frites and Belgian waffles.\n', 'Chocolate, Beer, Waffles, Architecture, History', 'Brussels', 'Brussels, Antwerp, Ghent, Bruges', 'Dutch, French, German', 'Euro', 'https://lp-cms-production.imgix.net/2022-05/GettyRF_597070535.jpg?auto=format&w=1920&h=640&fit=crop&crop=faces,edges&q=75'),
(20, 'Belize', 'BZ', 'Belize, located on the northeastern coast of Central America, is renowned for its stunning barrier reef, lush rainforests, and diverse wildlife. Visitors can snorkel or dive among colorful coral formations, explore ancient Mayan ruins like Caracol and Xunantunich, and immerse themselves in the rich culture of its Garifuna and Maya communities.\n', 'Reefs, Rainforest, Mayan, Adventure, Culture', 'Belmopan', 'Belmopan, Belize City, San Ignacio, Orange Walk Town', 'English', 'Belize Dollar', 'https://media.timeout.com/images/105239971/image.jpg'),
(21, 'Benin', 'BJ', 'Located in West Africa, Benin is known for its rich history, vibrant culture, and diverse landscapes. Visitors can explore ancient royal palaces in Abomey, witness traditional voodoo ceremonies, and relax on the pristine beaches along the Atlantic coast.\n', 'Voodoo, History, Culture, Nature, Markets', 'Porto-Novo', 'Porto-Novo, Cotonou, Parakou, Djougou', 'French', 'West African CFA franc', 'https://www.bradtguides.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ganvie-benin-laurent-nilles-scaled.jpg'),
(22, 'Bermuda', 'BM', 'A British Overseas Territory in the North Atlantic Ocean, Bermuda is famous for its pink-sand beaches, turquoise waters, and distinctive pastel-colored houses. Visitors can explore historic sites like the Royal Naval Dockyard, snorkel among shipwrecks in the crystal-clear waters, and enjoy world-class golfing and sailing.\n', 'Beaches, Pink Sand, History, Sailing, Triangle', 'Hamilton', 'Hamilton, St. George\'s, Somerset Village, Flatts Village', 'English', 'Bermudian Dollar', 'https://www.tripsavvy.com/thmb/dvgOg72VR2ghBTIekOnMdY6eMMQ=/1500x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/TimMLanthier-eced7b2434724a9a9bf3cc7733834c13.jpg'),
(23, 'Bhutan', 'BT', 'Nestled in the eastern Himalayas, Bhutan is known for its stunning mountain scenery, ancient monasteries, and unique cultural traditions. Visitors can trek through pristine landscapes, visit sacred sites like the Taktsang Monastery (Tiger\'s Nest), and experience the country\'s Gross National Happiness philosophy firsthand.\n', 'Himalayas, Monasteries, Happiness, Trekking, Culture', 'Thimphu', 'Thimphu, Phuntsholing, Paro, Punakha', 'Dzongkha', 'Ngultrum', 'https://good-nature-blog-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/2022/04/Bhutan-mountain-1-2.jpg'),
(24, 'Bolivia', 'BO', 'Situated in the heart of South America, Bolivia is known for its breathtaking landscapes, including the otherworldly Salar de Uyuni salt flats, the rugged Andean mountains, and the Amazon rainforest. Visitors can explore colonial cities like Sucre and Potosí, trek to ancient Inca ruins, and experience the rich culture of indigenous communities.\n', 'Andes, Salt Flats, Culture, Nature, Adventure', 'Sucre', 'La Paz, Santa Cruz, Cochabamba, Oruro', 'Spanish, Quechua, Aymara', 'Boliviano', 'https://www.state.gov/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/shutterstock_1030504030v2-2109x1406-1.jpg'),
(25, 'Bosnia & Herzegovina', 'BA', 'Located in the Balkans, Bosnia and Herzegovina is known for its stunning natural beauty, rich history, and diverse cultural heritage. Visitors can explore the historic streets of Sarajevo, marvel at the beauty of Mostar\'s Old Bridge, and discover hidden gems like the medieval town of Jajce and the picturesque village of Blagaj.\n', 'History, Ottoman, Nature, Culture, Cuisine', 'Sarajevo', 'Sarajevo, Banja Luka, Tuzla, Mostar', 'Bosnian, Croatian, Serbian', 'Convertible Mark', 'https://i.natgeofe.com/k/56db8db3-a139-41b9-885f-d3c5f3623343/bosnia-and-herzegovina-mostar-city_3x2.jpg?wp=1&w=1084.125&h=721.875'),
(26, 'Botswana', 'BW', 'A landlocked country in Southern Africa, Botswana is renowned for its vast wilderness areas, including the Okavango Delta, Chobe National Park, and the Kalahari Desert. Visitors can embark on safaris to see abundant wildlife such as elephants, lions, and giraffes, and experience the tranquility of the African bush.\n', 'Safari, Wildlife, Delta, Culture, Adventure', 'Gaborone', 'Gaborone, Francistown, Molepolole, Maun', 'English, Tswana', 'Pula', 'https://www.andbeyond.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/Herd-of-Elephants-walking-while-guests-cross-channel-on-a-Safari-Game-Drive-in-Botswana.jpg'),
(27, 'Brazil', 'BR', 'The largest country in South America, known for its Amazon rainforest, Christ the Redeemer statue, and Carnaval festival.', 'Amazon, Carnaval, Football, Beaches, Music', 'Brasília', 'São Paulo, Rio de Janeiro, Brasília, Salvador', 'Portuguese', 'Real', 'https://www.celebritycruises.com/blog/content/uploads/2021/09/what-is-brazil-known-for-christ-the-redeemer-aerial-hero.jpg'),
